headline: RBC Maintains Pepsico (PEP) Price Target and Sector Perform Rating
summary: Pepsico, Inc. (NASDAQ:PEP) is one of 10 consumer defensive stocks to buy now. RBC Capital held its Sector Perform rating on Pepsico, Inc. (NASDAQ:PEP) with a price target of $148, citing ongoing revenue headwinds for the food and beverage giant. The research firm pointed to the company’s “significant underperformance” as a source of concern among investors, […]
